 Laycon Set To Launch Reality TV Series ‘I Am Laycon’ (Source:Instagram/Laycon) Big Brother Naija’s season five winner, Laycon is returning to your TV screen this February for his anticipated reality show, ‘I Am Laycon’. The Showmax original show will premiere on February 11, 2021, exclusively on Showmax as the streamer’s first ever Nigerian production. ‘I Am Laycon’ will follow the reality star as he settles into his celebrity life. The show will also showcase Laycon’s personal relationships and an insight into his booming music career.